The Chronicle Flora Fadzai Sibanda, Online Reporter POLICE in Zvishavane are investigating a shooting incident that left a 27-year-old in hospital fighting for his life. In a tweet, police said the complainant was shot by an unknown suspect while walking with his friend along a strip road near Dadaya High School. He was shot in the stomach and was rushed to a local hospital in Zvishavane where he is getting treatment. @flora_sibanda 